    "description": "这是一款以“像素艺术与3D融合的视觉表现”为特色的3D冒险游戏<br>主人公为了寻找毫无预兆地消失的挚友，彷徨在逐渐消失的东京<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/5dddf284c12c5ed25e587b12fcfe6d14.poster.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/5dddf284c12c5ed25e587b12fcfe6d14.webm?t=1686992713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/5dddf284c12c5ed25e587b12fcfe6d14.mp4?t=1686992713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/6ea80560f3bf1d3d59ffa43625b4715a.poster.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/6ea80560f3bf1d3d59ffa43625b4715a.webm?t=1686992713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/6ea80560f3bf1d3d59ffa43625b4715a.mp4?t=1686992713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“她已经不在了，但她的故事还在这座城市里继续着”<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/f32ef9b61161a2384cb8e6e0b5b195ff.poster.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/f32ef9b61161a2384cb8e6e0b5b195ff.webm?t=1686992713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/f32ef9b61161a2384cb8e6e0b5b195ff.mp4?t=1686992713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>・故事<br>以“空无一人的东京”为舞台展开的一系列重叠的故事<br>挚友为何会从主人公面前消失？这座城市到底想要传达什么？众多片段聚集在一起，慢慢逼近真相的核心<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/8375a6b28ec30e2ca4c5f242b77fa036.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=260 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/3f98afcc18c18ba47eb4d3d0a55317cd.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=260 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/de7f8e4bd82dfdc5e0d04a619809ed33.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=260 /></span><br><br>・登场人物<br>为了找回突然消失的朋友，来到这座城市的主人公<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/9e441de09f57d56e33ee6724d70eaa74.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=260 /></span><br><br>为了隐藏不可告人的秘密，来到这座城市的青年<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/3f4e8c6b0dd7d5b1f1edf9d313f2f5ec.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=260 /></span><br><br>没有告诉任何人原因，就无故消失在这座城市里的少女<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/52ac532570f11c065d6f928dafe66b9a.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=260 /></span><br><br>他们编织的故事，慢慢地开始露出獠牙，<br>不久，一切就都堕入了令人意想不到的方向………<br><br>・游戏介绍<br>融合了像素艺术和3D的新感觉冒险游戏<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/dfb019c8e6b76a607e22d992ecf146f9.avif?t=1686992713\" width=540 height=260 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251970/extras/0bfc05af252f4bd1bbec01452249cb44.avif?t